snippet.title: Natalie Brooks: Secrets of the Treasure House
snippet.description:
Young Natalie Brooks inherits an old mansion from her grandmother. There are many hidden rooms and secret passages in this old house. Help Natalie to reveal all the secrets hidden in this old place. Help her to solve puzzles, find hidden objects and talk to different characters. What could be up with the strange superintended who does not seem to care about the law?.. You should find out now!
The game is available early 2010 in the UK.
